Summary(pl.UTF-8):	Analiza gigabajtów danych JSON na sekundę
Name:		simdjson
Version:	4.1.0
Release:	2
License:	Apache v2.0 or MIT
Group:		Libraries
#Source0Download: https://github.com/simdjson/simdjson/releases
